00:09:25.280 --> 00:09:26.320
I...

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:28.680
I'll do it myself.

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.440
Luo Zhenyao, go to hell.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:44.680
Yao.

00:09:44.680 --> 00:09:45.660
It's a misunderstanding.

00:09:46.160 --> 00:09:47.040
A misunderstanding.

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:49.840
Hey, Yao.

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:50.200
Don't...

00:09:50.250 --> 00:09:51.200
It's a misunderstanding.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:51.560
Yao.

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:52.440
